				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/accountability" title="View all posts in Accountability" rel="category tag">Accountability</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/current-affairs" title="View all posts in Current Affairs" rel="category tag">Current Affairs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/democracy" title="View all posts in Democracy" rel="category tag">Democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/gaddafi" title="View all posts in Gaddafi" rel="category tag">Gaddafi</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/isc" title="View all posts in ISC" rel="category tag">ISC</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/libya" title="View all posts in Libya" rel="category tag">Libya</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/machon" title="View all posts in Machon" rel="category tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mi6" title="View all posts in MI6" rel="category tag">MI6</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/national-security" title="View all posts in National security" rel="category tag">National security</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/terrorism" title="View all posts in Terrorism" rel="category tag">Terrorism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/torture" title="View all posts in Torture" rel="category tag">Torture</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title